mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:14.2500pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">· </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Peirce has been the only member of the SEC to voice opposition to </span><a href="https://www.okex.com/academy/en/bitcoin-bandwagoning-an-examination-of-institutional-investment-in-crypto?channelFlag=ACECO1500807"><u><span class="15" style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Bitcoin ETF application denials</span></u></a><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">. Should her second term be approved, the likelihood of ever seeing such an exchange-traded fund is, at the very least, not damaged.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
