margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">TRON’s TRX strongly resembles a security, says industry council</span></b><b><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 21pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class="p" style="margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">The Crypto Rating Council (CRC) has unofficially deemed Tron’s, Nervos’ and Polkadot’s respective tokens as facing a higher likelihood of being deemed securities under U.S. securities law, according to a mid-April rating list obtained by </span><a href="https://www.theblockcrypto.com/post/64569/crypto-ratings-preliminary-scores-trx-dot-ckb"><u><span class="15" style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">The Block</span></u></a><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">.</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">The unpublished rating list in question reportedly assigned a score to each token of 4.75 out of 5.00, which means that they strongly resemble securities.</span><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top:12.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span class="16" style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Key takeaways</span></b><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:9.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:9.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:14.2500pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">· </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The CRC was founded by Coinbase, Circle, Genesis Capital, and other high-profile crypto firms to provide clarity on regulatory issues surrounding cryptocurrencies. Thus, its assessment does not mean that TRX and others are actually securities in the eyes of regulators — only that the council has determined that they resemble them.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(79,86,105);font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:9.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:0.0000pt;
margin-left:9.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;line-height:14.2500pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">· </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">If the SEC was to hypothetically heed the CRC’s assessment, the Tron, Nervos and Polkadot ecosystems would likely undergo a tumultuous experience.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';color:rgb(79,86,105);font-size:12.0000pt;
