            array (
                'id' => 166,
                'article_id' => 82,
                'locale' => 'zh-CN',
                'title' => '莱特币（LTC）现状调查研究',
            'body' => '<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">（LTC）简介</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">1）莱特币（LTC）的前世今生</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">莱特币（Litecoin），简写LTC，货币符号Ł，创始者李启威（Charlie Lee），LTC代表着轻量级，是对比<a href="https://www.okex.me/academy/zh" class="seo-words" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; user-select: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105) !important;">比特币</a>来讲更为轻量级的数字货币。它与比特币（BTC）在技术上具有相同的实现原理，其创造和转让基于一种开源的加密协议，不受到任何中央机构的管理。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">历史大事记：</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2011年10月7日莱特币通过Github上面的开源客户端进行发布。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2015年8月26日，莱特币首次减半，每个区块产出量由50降至25个莱特币。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2016年7月3日，莱特币内核开发团队和莱特币协会发布了“莱特币官方2016年开发路线图”，宣称将发布带有“隔离见证”、“闪电网络”、“智能合约”等功能的新版本。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2017年5月11日，隔离见证在莱特币第1201536个区块正式激活，莱特币用户可使用隔离见证这种新的交易方式。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2017年6月21日，莱特币创始人正式宣布莱特币闪电网络上线。闪电网络本质上是使用了哈希时间锁定智能合约来安全地进行0确认交易的一种机制。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">莱特币拥有完整的产业链和充分的流动性，全球莱特币ATM的数量仅次于比特币，矿工和算力、交易平台、开发者、接受支付的商家和粉丝持续增长。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">2）莱特币的机制</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">莱特币被称为是“数字白银”，是第一个基于Scrypt算法的网络数字货币，与比特币相比，莱特币具有三个显著差异：</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（1）莱特币网络每2.5分钟（而不是10分钟）就可以处理一个块，提供更快的交易确认。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（2）莱特币网络预期产出8400万个莱特币，是比特币发行货币量的四倍。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（3）莱特币在工作量证明算法中使用了由Colin Percival首次提出的Scrypt加密算法，相比于比特币使用的SHA256算法，Scrypt算法对挖掘处理能力要求不高，只需要高速访问内存，更容易在普通计算机上挖矿。Scrpyt算法由于其内存依赖的设计特别符合对抗专业矿机的设计，成为数字货币算法发展的一个主要应用方向。Scrpyt算法提醒了人们对于算力中心化的认识，开启了人们对于hash计算去中心化安全的探索，促进了区块链系统向更好的方向发展。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">3）莱特币减产</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">每4年，莱特币将进行减产，每个区块挖出的莱特币减半，上一次减半发生在2015年8月26日，莱特币的区块奖励由50个减半到25个。产量减半从理论上来说会导致供需不平衡，价格上涨，但实际情况却有很多影响因素，15年莱特币减半从其价格表现上可以看出，减半后并没有发生价格上涨，反而有些跌幅。从今天的视角看过去，有几个原因可以作为解释。</p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-cd8e64b89b9411fdb6db2818fb2e548b_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">2015年LTC减半前后两个月的走势</figcaption></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一是在这之前，LTC已经进行了充分的上涨，7月10日曾达到当时最高点8.967美金，市场预期已经得到了充分的体现。二是当时整个数字货币的体量还十分小，应用场景也很有限，过度的炒作使其价格过多偏离价值，实际需求占比很小，减半影响甚微。第三，当价格没有上涨的情况下，减半致使矿工立减一半，高成本的矿工将入不敷出，只得选择关机。而实际上，LTC算力在减半后有一定幅度的下降，价格受此影响反而持续走低。因此8月27日，莱特币已经迎来了减半之后的第一次难度调整，降低7.61%。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这是发生在2015年的历史，历史不代表未来，现在整个加密货币市场已经不能同日而语，LTC也是如此，接下来stai Research将就LTC目前的状况做全面的研究和分析。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">2. 莱特币（LTC）的现状</span></p><div class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><figure class="aligncenter" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-3e53fccac28b5563c5dd7deeec17073f_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">LTC目前基本情况</figcaption></figure></div><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">LTC总供给量8400万个，目前已经挖出6100多万个，现价60美金一个，总市值36.7亿美金，排名第四。</p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-418b0d859e519eaf5e18bd6d5933c668_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">LTC历史价格走势</figcaption></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">链上交易情况</span></p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-fcfc60d9625909a3f684924b6b72ec13_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">LTC等币种链上交易数据对比</figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6eb29744cf7606be7c773afed5b7e628_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">近3个月LTC平均手续费</figcaption></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">LTC链上交易数与交易额相较于BTC、ETH还有不少差距，但考虑到其市值和用户群体规模，以及24小时交易额能够占到总市值的5.51%，并有55822个活跃地址，LTC的链上交易可以说还是相当活跃的，尤其近三个月，从其交易手续费的走势可以看出，链上交易在逐渐活跃并保持着增长。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">LTC分布情况</span></p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-3e3cecfb8e1472c7ecbe669a6d0c7e61_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">LTC分配情况</figcaption></figure><div class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><figure class="aligncenter" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4cf58f15e253157b9c6cd1a619c31a9c_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">前10、100、1000地址持币占比</figcaption></figure></div><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">LTC的分配情况显示出目前加密货币领域的通病，大量的筹码集中在少数头部的地址当中，前500位地址占据LTC近60%的量，但相较于其他小币种，LTC地址的分配情况已经较为分散，跟大部分主流币的情况差不多，并且这其中包涵了中心化交易所的地址。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">LTC矿池</span></p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-c5e1dacb4a58fda780041037e6930509_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">LTC矿池份额</figcaption></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">LTC矿池份额占比基本都比较均有，最高的F2Pool占比20.45%，前几大矿池的占比都比较接近，这有利于维护币种的安全和矿工的利益，而全网总共269.77TH/s的算力，相较于BTC 47.31 EH/s和BCH 1.6EH/s还是有一定的差距。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-4e9c82fa65f3e03247a533d1381afdac_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">LTC最后100个区块的哈希分配</figcaption></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">Github代码更新频率</span></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-attachment-id="2154" data-permalink="https://www.okex.me/academy/zh/litecoin-the-silver-to-bitcoins-gold-i-cn/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd" data-orig-file="https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd.jpg" data-orig-size="720,386" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{"aperture":"0","credit":"","camera":"","caption":"","created_timestamp":"0","copyright":"","focal_length":"0","iso":"0","shutter_speed":"0","title":"","orientation":"0"}" data-image-title="v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd-300x161.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd.jpg" src="https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-be4c01ad6014674a4a64a67e9155145a_hd.jpg" alt="preview" class="wp-image-2154" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">LTC在Github代码更新频率一直保持不错的情况，最近三个月有所减缓。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">谷歌指数</span></p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c5da5ccebaab0cad04de6e34ce2d281f_hd.jpg" alt="" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">谷歌趋势</figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-attachment-id="2156" data-permalink="https://www.okex.me/academy/zh/litecoin-the-silver-to-bitcoins-gold-i-cn/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd" data-orig-file="https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd.jpg" data-orig-size="720,243" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{"aperture":"0","credit":"","camera":"","caption":"","created_timestamp":"0","copyright":"","focal_length":"0","iso":"0","shutter_speed":"0","title":"","orientation":"0"}" data-image-title="v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd-300x101.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd.jpg" src="https://www.okex.me/academy/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/v2-bc1eca27b5513976c6e712159a00a7c6_hd.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-2156" style="padding: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 8px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(245, 246, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(233, 235, 242); height: auto;"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;">谷歌趋势分布</figcaption></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">从谷歌趋势可以看出，LTC近一年的热度在主流币当中都是处于较高的位置，而关注LTC的地区主要集中在美洲和欧洲，尤其在美国、加拿大和维瑞内拉。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;">结论</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">从以上数据基本可以一览LTC整个项目目前的基本情况，从其链活跃程度、分配情况、矿池份额、算力、代码更新、谷歌趋势可以看出，LTC整条链保持良好的运行情况，作为市值排名第四的加密货币，其链上活跃程度、去中心化程度以及谷歌趋势相较于其他主流币种也有不错的表现，但同样，加密货币的通病在其身上也有充分的体现。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">不过，这仅仅是一些表面数据的罗列和展现，下篇我们将会对LTC的通证循环、挖矿机制、支付生态及其落地模块进展做详细的分析和讨论</p>',
