                'title' => 'Bitcoin Back Above $11K as USDT Flows Continue and Futures Basis Surges — Crypto Market Daily',
            'body' => '<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">After a brief pullback, Bitcoin (<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.okex.com/markets/index/btc-usd" target="_blank" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;">BTC</a>) saw a further appreciation in the last 24 hours, going up 1.12% to trade around $11,030, as per the STAI BTC Index price. The overall trend in Bitcoin remains strong, generally buoying the market and helping large-cap coins make important breakthroughs.</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Bitcoin Cash (<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.okex.com/markets/index/bch-usd" target="_blank" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;">BCH</a>), for instance, surpassed its previous high of $280 and continued to move up quickly to its current level near $293, rising 7.54% in the last 24 hours. The BCH/BTC pair also reached two-month highs of 0.0269 last night. This breakout may attract more traders to join and thus keep the rally going. </p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.okex.com/markets/index/eos-usd" target="_blank" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;">EOS</a> and XRP, on the other hand, respectively surged 10.73% and 8.17%, and both have reached new highs since April 29. Ether (ETH), which broke out recently to cross the $300 level, currently stands at $321 — up a relatively modest 1.57% in the last 24 hours.</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The rise in large-caps also drove up the total cryptocurrency market capitalization by 1.5% to $331 billion, while Bitcoin\'s dominance fell by 0.2% and is now at 61.4%, according to data from <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.coingecko.com/en" target="_blank" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;">CoinGecko</a>. </p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Meanwhile, stock markets retreated on Tuesday, with the Nasdaq Composite Index down 1.27% and the S&P 500 down 0.65%. Gold futures prices rose for the second day in a row, however, hitting another record close and intraday high. Moreover, the Federal Reserve has been holding a two-day meeting that started Tuesday, with the results of the meeting to be announced on Wednesday.</p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21864c67e26.jpg" alt="OKEx Token Index Board as of 8:00 am UTC on 7/29/20. Source: OKEx" style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" width="800" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21864c67e26.jpg"><br><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;"><em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;"><span style="color: rgb(79, 86, 105); font-size: 16px; text-align: start;">STAI</span> Token Index Board as of 8:00 am UTC on 7/29/20. Source: </em><span style="color: rgb(79, 86, 105); font-size: 16px; text-align: start;">STAI</span></figcaption></figure><h2 style="padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(25, 32, 47); line-height: 1.2; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">A hint of risk in a lot of good numbers</h2><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The amount of USDT flowing into exchanges recently spiked to a yearly high, according to on-chain data provider <a href="https://twitter.com/glassnode/status/1287805348389232640" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;">Glassnode</a>, and Tether <a href="https://news.huoxing24.com/flash/20200729163235244589.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;">issued</a> another $300 million USDT around an hour ago today. This USDT issuance hints at increasing market demand and could potentially support further Bitcoin price appreciation.</p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21866271526.jpg" alt="USDT Exchange Inflow. Source: Glassnode" style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" width="800" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21866271526.jpg"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;"><em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;">USDT Exchange Inflow. Source: </em><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://twitter.com/glassnode/status/1287805348389232640" target="_blank" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;"><em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;">Glassnode</em></a></figcaption></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Looking at futures data, STAI one-month futures annualized basis surged to as high as 25.67% yesterday, its highest level since late February, as per data by skew. Values above 20% indicate that traders are paying a very high premium on spots and using high leverage. </p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f2186794fe6a.jpg" alt="BTC Futures Annualized Rolling 1-Month Basis. Source: skew" style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" width="800" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f2186794fe6a.jpg"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;"><em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;">BTC Futures Annualized Rolling 1-Month Basis. Source: </em><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://analytics.skew.com/dashboard/okex" target="_blank" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(33, 77, 237); user-select: none;"><em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;">skew</em></a></figcaption></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">At the same time, we note that funding rates for perpetual swaps have been at high levels since Monday. With most traders in profit due to the price increase, the higher funding rates can still be maintained for some time. However, highly leveraged traders may find it difficult to maintain their current positions for prolonged periods.</p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(31, 34, 54); font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21868e1722a.jpg" alt="Funding Rates. Data Collection Time: 7/27 0:00 am UTC to 7/29 8:00 am UTC" style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" width="800" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/030d7e8e966169ab4c7f67c291c333f45f21868e1722a.jpg"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: rgb(34, 42, 60); line-height: 20px;"><em style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none;">Funding Rates. Data Collection Time: 7/27 0:00 am UTC to 7/29 8:00 am UTC</em></figcaption></figure>',
