            'body' => '<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">涨跌有趋势，读懂价格语言；</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">买卖有信号，告别感觉交易。<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">本节我们继续学习K线的组合应用——看跌组合。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">夕阳无限好，已是近黄昏。黄昏之星的出现，预示币价上涨行情告一段落，调整即将来临。<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">什么样的K线组合是黄昏之星呢？如图红色画线处所示。<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">标准的黄昏之星由三根K线组合而成，首先是一根较大的阳线，随后紧跟一根类似“十字”的星线，第三根K线是一根较大的阴线。黄昏之星是否成立，对第三根阴线的长度有着明确的要求，它的收盘价格一定要低于第一根阳线实体的50%。<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在确定黄昏之星有效以后，我们可以通过最后一根阴线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看跌力度强弱。如图，阴线收盘价格刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下的看跌力度比较弱。若后阴线收盘价格与前阳线开盘价格持平，则认为看跌力度较强。若后阴线收盘价格明显低于前阳线开盘价格，则认为看跌力度相当强劲。<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">刚刚所讲是最标准的黄昏之星组合，但在实际走势中，黄昏之星会有一些变化。那么市场中真实的黄昏之星是怎样的呢？</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">例如图示三种黄昏之星的样子，图一，中间由两根小K线组成。我们将它还原到实际走势图中。币价在大涨之后的高位区出现黄昏之星，后市币价出现大幅调整。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">图二，中间K线并不是标准的十字星线，而是带有长上影线的小K线。在高位出现黄昏之星后，币价滞涨回落</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">图三，中间出现两根十字星，阴线力度明显大于阳线。币价在大涨后出现看跌力度强劲的黄昏之星，在高位震荡后最终出现大跌。有些时候黄昏之星会连续出现两个，甚至更多。BTC/USDT这段下跌走势途中，相隔不远的两个反弹高位都出现了黄昏之星，币价随后继续下跌。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">接下来我们学习第二种看跌K线组合--看跌吞没。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">首先，看一下看跌吞没的特征。后一根阴线实体，完全覆盖前一根阳线实体，如同阳线被阴线吞噬掉一般。说明空头力量正在大举反攻。因此得名看跌吞没。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">那么如何判断看跌力度呢？<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">图一，下跌阴线实体刚刚将阳线实体吞没，该种情况看跌力度较弱；图二，阴线实体收盘价明显低于阳线开盘价，阴线长度甚至达到阳线的两倍，该种情况看跌力度很强；图三，阴线实体一举将多根阳线吞没，该种情况看跌力度非常强劲。<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在市场中存在很多非标准的看跌吞没组合，那实际的看跌吞没组合是怎样的呢？</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">例如三种看跌吞没组合的变体。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一，币价大幅上涨后出现了一阴吞多阳的强劲看跌吞没组合后，币价出现连续下跌。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">二，在下跌行情的反弹高点，出现看跌吞没组合，币价结束反弹继续下行。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">三，币价在连续大涨后，出现看跌吞没组合，随后展开大幅下跌。<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">第三种看跌K线组合：塔形顶</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">塔形顶，左边是一根中阳线或大阳线；中间由若干根小k线组成，通常在5根以上；右边是一根中阴线或大阴线。整体看上去就像一座宝塔，因此得名塔形顶。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一个有效的塔形顶要满足：最后一根阴线的收盘价要低于前面大阴线实体的50%以下；塔形顶所展现的是：市场中做多力量逐步衰竭，多空达成平衡，最后到下跌力度增强的过程。<span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在确定塔形顶有效后，我们可以通过最后一根阴线收盘价的位置，来判断后市看跌力度的强弱。如图，若阴线收盘价刚刚超过50%及格线，那么这种情况下看跌力度相对比较弱；若后阴线收盘价基本与前阳线开盘价持平，则认为看跌力度较强；若后阴线收盘价明显低于前阳线开盘价，则看跌力度相当强劲。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">当然，在实际走势中塔形顶并不像我们示意图中展示的这么完美。要活学活用。我们看一下市场实际中的塔形顶是怎样的。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">变化一，中间多根小K线带有长影线。在大幅度上涨后出现塔形顶组合，之后币价连续下跌，并跌穿前期低点。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">变化二，塔形顶中间部分并不都是非常小的K线构成，K线震荡幅度较大。币价在一段反弹行情中出现塔形顶，随后继续大幅下跌。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">最后我们回顾一下本期内容：</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: rgb(79, 86, 105); line-height: 1.5; font-family: "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Icons", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">三种典型的看跌组合。第一种，黄昏之星，预示黑暗即将降临；第二种，看跌吞没，空头力挽狂澜；第三种，塔形顶，多头逐步缴械投降。</p>',
                'excerpt' => '零基礎學習幣市分析| 4 看跌K線組合',
            ),
