ap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;">SNX</a>) bounced 16.77% today. Loopring (<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/lrc-usdt" target="_blank" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;" data-mce-href="https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/lrc-usdt" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;">LRC</a>) ranked third, gaining 12.49%. </p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">The biggest loser today is HyperDAO (<a href="https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/hdao-usdt" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;" data-mce-href="https://www.okex.com/markets/spot-info/hdao-usdt" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; cursor: pointer; color: #214ded; user-select: none;">HDAO</a>), which is down 12.30%.</p><h2 style="padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;">BTC technical analysis</h2><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">Bitcoin is now starting a retracement phase after hitting prices above $11,000. Because the price has surpassed the critical $10,500 resistance level, we need to pay attention to the short-term threshold of $10,670. Midterm critical support is located at $10,280. </p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">The next price target for the first and foremost cryptocurrency is at $11,400 — but high funding rates remain a potential roadblock to price increases.</p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;" contenteditable="false" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg" width="800" height="425" alt="" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg"><br></figure><h2 style="padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;">ETH technical analysis</h2><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">The upward momentum has slowed for the price of ETH, but the bullish trend in the midterm remains intact. A continuation of the uptrend after a short-term correction is still promising. </p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">An intraday support level is around $299. As long as it holds this price, we may see another test of the previous high of $334. Because ETH has risen very quickly in the early going, profit-taking could impose a lot of pressure in the short-term. </p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;" contenteditable="false" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg" alt="OKEx ETH Perpetual Swap 1h chart – 7/28/20. Source: OKEx, TradingView" style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" width="800" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; max-width: 100%; background: #f5f6fa; border: 1px solid #e9ebf2; height: 425px; margin: 30px 0px 8px 0px;" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg"><figcaption style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;" contenteditable="true" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; color: #222a3c; line-height: 20px;"><br></figcaption></figure><h2 style="padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 40px 0px 0px; font-size: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; font-weight: 500; color: #19202f; line-height: 1.2;">LTC technical analysis</h2><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">LTC has surged 10% in the last 24 hours as trading volumes have amplified. The intraday threshold is sitting around $52.50. Given the higher historical correlation between LTC and BTC, it is also important to be aware of Bitcoin\'s short-term movements when trading LTC.</p><figure class="wp-block-image" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;" contenteditable="false" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; color: #1f2236;"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg" width="800" height="425" alt="" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/648b9906a614a4bb30c20591243c65ec5f218bb1665df.jpg"><br></figure><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-sty