            array (
                'id' => 190,
                'article_id' => 90,
                'locale' => 'zh-CN',
                'title' => '零基础学习币市分析| 2 单根K线的演变及寓意',
                'body' => '<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">涨跌有趋势，读懂价格语言；</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">买卖有信号，告别感觉交易。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">上一章节，我们初步认识了K线及其结构，可认识K线有什么用呢？续课程，我将逐步为大家揭晓答案。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">今天我们一起学习单根K线的演变和寓意。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">首先来看一下，K线在连续的价格变化中是如何演变的。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">图为“一字线”，开盘价与收盘价为同一价格。常常出现在开盘瞬间、成交非常匮乏时 或 股市开盘封涨跌停时。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">伴随市场的逐渐活跃，价格出现变动。形成图示实体较短的“小K线”。左边表示价格上涨，通常称为“小阳线”，右边表示价格下跌，通常称为“小阴线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">越发活跃的市场，形成图示实体较长的“中阳线”和“中阴线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">该时段交易极度活跃，形成左边“大阳线”和右边“大阴线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">那么影线是如何形成的呢？</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">我们回到刚刚开盘的样子。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/92a5baa64f0c39a0233f9f53c7c124315f2194668cdd2.png" width="803" height="501" alt="" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/92a5baa64f0c39a0233f9f53c7c124315f2194668cdd2.png"></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">价格逐渐下跌。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">当价格跌至某一价格时，市场逐渐出现主动买入的投资者，将价格一步一步推升上去，形成下影线。如图K线实体较小，只有下影线的K线，通常称为“锤子线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">当左图的K线实体成为一条细线时，我们称为“T字线”。右图为我们前面所讲的“一字线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">随着买入力量越来越强，币价逐渐上涨，形成图示两种看涨阳线。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">当价格上涨至一定高度，市场逐渐出现主动卖出的投资者，将币价慢慢打压下去，形成上影线，如图所示。右图K线实体较小，只有上影线的K线，通常称为“倒锤线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">卖盘逐渐增加，打压价格继续下跌，最终收盘价格与开盘价格相同。如图所示，左图形如十字架的K线称为“十字星线”，右图因其形似墓碑，通常称为“墓碑线”，也可以叫“倒T字线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">我们通过K线的一步步变化，认识了很多K线，那K线一共有多少种样子呢？</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">这些K线又应该如何分类呢？</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">如图所示，我们将各式各样的K线有序排列在一起。横竖相乘，一共42种。我们先说明K线实体长短的寓意。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/c65deff802f5bef7faf539a374ab723c5f21947b2a65c.png" width="801" height="503" alt="" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/c65deff802f5bef7faf539a374ab723c5f21947b2a65c.png"></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第一行，实体短的绿色小阳线，寓意上涨力量软弱。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第二行，实体较长的绿色中阳线，寓意上涨力量强。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第三行，实体很长的绿色大阳线，寓意上涨力量占据绝对优势。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第四行，实体呈细线状，统称星线，寓意多空争夺激烈，势均力敌。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第五行，实体短的红色小阴线，寓意下跌力量软弱。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第六行，实体较长的红色中阴线，寓意下跌力量强。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第七行，实体很长的红色大阴线，寓意下跌力量占据绝对优势。接下来我们揭开上下影线长短的寓意。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第一列，K线无上下影线，我们通常称为光头光脚，寓意局势一边倒。阳线表示多头强势，阴线表示空头强势。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第二列，只有下影线，看起来像K线没长头发，因此常叫秃顶。寓意下有支撑，下影线越长，支撑越强。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第三列，K线只有上影线，通常称为赤脚。寓意上有阻力，上影线越长，阻力越强。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第四列，上下影线长度几乎相等，寓意支撑与阻力均有，且旗鼓相当。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第五列，下影线较上影线长些，寓意下方支撑大于上方阻力。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">第六列，上影线较下影线长，寓意上方阻力大于下方支撑。将无数组这样的K线排列在一起，就构成了我们常看到的价格走势图。</p>',
