                'body' => '<p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">涨跌有趋势，读懂价格语言；</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">买卖有信号，告别感觉交易。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">上一章节，我们初步认识了K线及其结构，可认识K线有什么用呢？续课程，我将逐步为大家揭晓答案。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">今天我们一起学习单根K线的演变和寓意。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">首先来看一下，K线在连续的价格变化中是如何演变的。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">图为“一字线”，开盘价与收盘价为同一价格。常常出现在开盘瞬间、成交非常匮乏时 或 股市开盘封涨跌停时。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">伴随市场的逐渐活跃，价格出现变动。形成图示实体较短的“小K线”。左边表示价格上涨，通常称为“小阳线”，右边表示价格下跌，通常称为“小阴线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">越发活跃的市场，形成图示实体较长的“中阳线”和“中阴线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">该时段交易极度活跃，形成左边“大阳线”和右边“大阴线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">那么影线是如何形成的呢？</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">我们回到刚刚开盘的样子。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">价格逐渐下跌。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;">当价格跌至某一价格时，市场逐渐出现主动买入的投资者，将价格一步一步推升上去，形成下影线。如图K线实体较小，只有下影线的K线，通常称为“锤子线”。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/92a5baa64f0c39a0233f9f53c7c124315f2194ba34ebe.png" width="803" height="501" alt="" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/92a5baa64f0c39a0233f9f53c7c124315f2194ba34ebe.png"></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">當左圖的K線實體成為一條細線時，我們稱為“T字線”。右圖為我們前面所講的“一字線”。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">隨著買入力量越來越強，幣價逐漸上漲，形成圖示兩種看漲陽線。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">當價格上漲至一定高度，市場逐漸出現主動賣出的投資者，將幣價慢慢打壓下去，形成上影線，如圖所示。右圖K線實體較小，只有上影線的K線，通常稱為“倒錘線”。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">賣盤逐漸增加，打壓價格繼續下跌，最終收盤價格與開盤價格相同。如圖所示，左圖形如十字架的K線稱為“十字星線”，右圖因其形似墓碑，通常稱為“墓碑線”，也可以叫“倒T字線”。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">我們通過K線的一步步變化，認識了很多K線，那K線一共有多少種樣子呢？</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">這些K線又應該如何分類呢？</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">如圖所示，我們將各式各樣的K線有序排列在一起。橫豎相乘，一共42種。我們先說明K線實體長短的寓意。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><img src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/c65deff802f5bef7faf539a374ab723c5f2194cd0d276.png" width="801" height="503" alt="" data-mce-src="http://qkladmin2.ruanmeng.top/storage/tinymce/images/c65deff802f5bef7faf539a374ab723c5f2194cd0d276.png"></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第一行，實體短的綠色小陽線，寓意上漲力量軟弱。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第二行，實體較長的綠色中陽線，寓意上漲力量強。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第三行，實體很長的綠色大陽線，寓意上漲力量佔據絕對優勢。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第四行，實體呈細線狀，統稱星線，寓意多空爭奪激烈，勢均力敵。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第五行，實體短的紅色小陰線，寓意下跌力量軟弱。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第六行，實體較長的紅色中陰線，寓意下跌力量強。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第七行，實體很長的紅色大陰線，寓意下跌力量佔據絕對優勢。接下來我們揭開上下影線長短的寓意。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第一列，K線無上下影線，我們通常稱為光頭光腳，寓意局勢一邊倒。陽線表示多頭強勢，陰線表示空頭強勢。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第二列，只有下影線，看起來像K線沒長頭髮，因此常叫禿頂。寓意下有支撐，下影線越長，支撐越強。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第三列，K線只有上影線，通常稱為赤腳。寓意上有阻力，上影線越長，阻力越強。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第四列，上下影線長度幾乎相等，寓意支撐與阻力均有，且旗鼓相當。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第五列，下影線較上影線長些，寓意下方支撐大於上方阻力。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="padding: 0px; margin: 16px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; color: #4f5669; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="color: #4f5669;">第六列，上影線較下影線長，寓意上方阻力大於下方支撐。將無數組這樣的K線排列在一起，就構成了我們常看到的價格走勢圖。</span></p>',
                'excerpt' => '零基礎學習幣市分析| 2 單根K線的演變及寓意',
