                'locale' => 'zh-TW',
                'title' => '比特幣看起來超買，但分析師淡化了對下跌的恐懼',
            'body' => '<div id="node-0"><p>隨著本周比特幣升至11個月來的最高水准，一些投資者開始擔心該加密貨幣超買，並且可能由於價格大幅下跌而引起。</p><p>但分析人士認為，這是一種過度反應。</p><p>根據CoinDesk的比特幣價格指數，比特幣的價格週一上漲至11319美元，為2019年8月以來的最高水准。</p><p>在撰寫本文時，該加密貨幣的交易價格接近11100美元，較一周前觀察到的9400美元的低點上漲了18%。</p><p>突然的反彈將14天相對强度指數（RSI）推高至80.00以上。</p><p>超過70.00的度量被認為是超買，這意味著看漲移動現在已被過度拉伸。</p></div><div id="node-3"><figure><div><div><picture data-image-id="499096"><source media="(min-width: 415px)" sizes="(min-width: 415px) 775px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png?format=webp 775w" type="image/webp"><source media="(min-width: 415px)" sizes="(min-width: 415px) 775px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png?format=jp2 775w" type="image/jp2"><source media="(min-width: 415px)" sizes="(min-width: 415px) 775px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png 775w" type="image/png"><source media="(max-width: 414px)" sizes="(max-width: 414px) 285px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png?format=webp 285w" type="image/webp"><source media="(max-width: 414px)" sizes="(max-width: 414px) 285px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png?format=jp2 285w" type="image/jp2"><source media="(max-width: 414px)" sizes="(max-width: 414px) 285px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-855x386.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-570x257.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-285x129.png 285w" type="image/png"><img width="775" height="350" src="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png" alt="第3天" loading="lazy" data-mce-src="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Dailies-775x350.png"></picture></div></div><figcaption><small>比特币价格日线图</small></figcaption><figcaption><small>资料来源：TradingView</small></figcaption></figure></div><div id="node-4"><ul><li><br></li><li>總部位於倫敦的Eterna Capital的首席首席投資官阿西姆·艾哈邁德（Asim Ahmad）表示，RSI高於70並不一定意味著即將出現的價格大幅下跌。<br></li><li>艾哈邁德說，這更有可能表明看漲行動過度，容易受到盤整或在最壞情况下的小幅回檔。<br></li><li>Stack基金的研究首長Lennard Neo解釋說，在一個強勁的趨勢市場中，RSI可以在較長時期內保持通脹，並補充說其他名額顯示出強勁的購買勢頭。<br></li><li>RSI基於價格，在之前的多頭交易中保持較高水準。</li></ul></div><div id="node-5"><h2>巩固合并？</h2></div><div id="node-6"><figure><div><div><picture data-image-id="499099"><source media="(min-width: 415px)" sizes="(min-width: 415px) 775px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png?format=webp 775w" type="image/webp"><source media="(min-width: 415px)" sizes="(min-width: 415px) 775px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png?format=jp2 775w" type="image/jp2"><source media="(min-width: 415px)" sizes="(min-width: 415px) 775px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png 775w" type="image/png"><source media="(max-width: 414px)" sizes="(max-width: 414px) 285px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png?format=webp 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png?format=webp 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png?format=webp 285w" type="image/webp"><source media="(max-width: 414px)" sizes="(max-width: 414px) 285px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png?format=jp2 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png?format=jp2 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png?format=jp2 285w" type="image/jp2"><source media="(max-width: 414px)" sizes="(max-width: 414px) 285px" srcset="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-855x385.png 855w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-570x257.png 570w, https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-285x128.png 285w" type="image/png"><img width="775" height="349" src="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png" alt="下载-6-43" loading="lazy" data-mce-src="https://static.coindesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/download-6-1-775x349.png"></picture></div></div><figcaption><small>2019年和2017年历史比特币日线图</small></figcaption><figcaption><small>资料来源：TradingView</small></figcaption></figure></div><div id="node-7"><ul><li>儘管RSI在三個月期間多次多次印出高於70.00的高價，但比特幣仍保持買價，並在2019年第二季度（左上）上漲了160%。<br></li><li>在2017年的牛市狂潮中觀察到了類似的模式（右上）。<br></li><li>回2020年夏季，RSI的超買名額可能會使加密貨幣在一段時間內徘徊在11000美元左右。支撐比特在10500美元左右。<br></li><li>Neo表示，將資金從DeFi領域和傳統市場轉移到比特幣將為加密貨幣創造動力。<br></li><li>如果美聯儲暗示對通貨膨脹的容忍度更高，那麼短期內價格可能會迅速升至12000美元。這可能會使美元再次遭到拋售，並使黃金價格突破2000美元大關。<br></li><li>LMAX Digital的貨幣策略師喬爾·克魯格（Joel Kruger）表示，比特幣仍然容易受到股票拋售的影響，正如三月份大盤崩盤時所看到的那樣。</li></ul></div>',
                'excerpt' => '隨著本周比特幣升至11個月來的最高水准，一些投資者開始擔心該加密貨幣超買，並且可能由於價格大幅下跌而引起。',
