            'body' => '<div id="node-0" class="article-pharagraph" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static !important;"><p class="text " style="margin: 0px 0px 41px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.42;"><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">尽管领先的加密货币</font><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">周一</font><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">的每日涨幅</font></font><a href="https://www.coindesk.com/gold-reaches-all-time-high-as-bitcoin-breaks-above-11k" data-reactroot="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;">超过10％，</a><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">但已结算的比特币期货合约仍保持在相对较低的水平，</font><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">因为一些交易员预计价格会上涨。</font></font></p></div><div id="node-1" class="article-list" style="margin: 40px 0px 42px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><ul style="margin: 24px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style-type: none;"><li style="margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;"><a href="https://qa.coindesk.com/price/bitcoin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-reactroot="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;">比特币</a><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">以上$ 11,400飙升，周一，但这种波动只能引发破产现价仅售$ 133万美元的比特币BitMEX期货合约的，领先的比特币衍生产品交易所，根据</font><a href="http://skew.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-reactroot="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(96, 138, 216); cursor: pointer;">偏移</a><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">。</font></li><li style="margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;"><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">自从2019年9月以来，比特币一直保持在该价格以下，对于许多交易员来说，突破10500美元是一个关键的看涨市场信号。</font></li><li style="margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;"><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">周一的清算还不到5月10日清算所关闭的合约数量的一半，当时比特币从每日开盘价9,500美元短暂下跌了15％，至8,100美元。</font></li><li style="margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;"><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">显着的比特币价格变动通常会达到随着时间的推移积累或以过度杠杆交易的市场流动性，触发数亿期货合约的清算。</font></li><li style="margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;"><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">加密货币交易公司Zorax Capital的执行合伙人Zoran Scekic说：“每个人都知道情况会加剧。”他补充说，他认为目前零售交易员并没有过度利用杠杆空头，这可能是相对较低的原因清算期货合约的水平。</font></li><li style="margin: 18px 0px 18px 82px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; list-style: none; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56; position: relative;"><font style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; vertical-align: inherit;">Scekic预计，由于市场情绪转为看涨，因此在首次适度的价格修正时会出现“大量清算”。</font></li></ul></div><div id="node-2" class="inline-image-v2 default" style="margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><figure style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 775px; width: max-content;"><div class="image-lightbox-wrapper" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; cursor: zoom-in;"><span class="expand-lightbox-icon-holder" style="margin: 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; z-index: 1; position: absolute; bottom: 10px; right: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; background-image: initial; backgrou