;"><p class="text " style="margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(22, 31, 54); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.56;">“There are some signs of upside exhaustion on this push higher, so we would be sure to await confirmation of the breakout before adding exposure to bitcoin. This would occur on consecutive weekly closes above $10,055,” she added.&nbsp;</p></div><div id="node-7" class="inline-image-v2 default" style="margin: 40px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; justify-content: center; color: rgb(25, 40, 77); font-family: acumin-pro, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><figure style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 775px; width: max-content;"><div class="image-lightbox-wrapper" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; cursor: zoom-in;"><span class="expand-lightbox-icon-holder" style="margin: 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; box-sizing: inherit; z-index: 1; position: absolute; bottom: 10px; right: 10px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; width: 40px; height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg class="svg-icon" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><path d="M19.5,-3.55271368e-15 L20,-3.55271368e-15 L20,0.5 L20,7.5 L19,7.5 L19,1.827 L11.8427091,8.38850444 L11.1572909,7.66035488 L18.42,1 L11.5,1 L11.5,-3.55271368e-15 L19.5,-3.55271368e-15 Z M0.5,20 L-1.13686838e-13,20 L-1.13686838e-13,19.5 L-1.13686838e-13,12.5 L1,12.5 L1,18.173 L8.15729086,11.6114956 L8.8